A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Councilwoman Hue Nguyen for her service to the City of
2 Morrow; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Councilwoman Hue Nguyen has served with distinction on the Morrow City
4 Council since her election in January 2024, earning recognition as the youngest current
5 council member and a dedicated advocate for progress in her community; and
6 WHEREAS, since assuming office, Councilwoman Hue Nguyen has focused on fostering
7 economic development, improving city parks, and enhancing community engagement to
8 better serve the residents of Morrow; and
9 WHEREAS, a proud resident of Morrow since 2002, she originally immigrated from
10 Vietnam and soon after began building after-school youth programs aimed at uplifting the
11 community and creating opportunities for all residents; and
12 WHEREAS, she further serves her community through her volunteer work at food pantries
13 and senior centers, grant writing and program administration for welfare initiatives, and her
14 leadership as a Sunday school teacher promoting education and cultural awareness; and
