15 WHEREAS, Councilwoman Hue Nguyen continues to be a tireless advocate for inclusion,
16 opportunity, and representation, ensuring that diverse voices are heard and valued in local
17 government and throughout the Morrow community; and
18 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this exemplary individual be
19 appropriately honored during this special time.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
21 recognize and commend Councilwoman Hue Nguyen for her efficient, effective, and
22 dedicated public service to the City of Morrow as well as extend best wishes for continued
23 success.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
25 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Councilwoman
26 Hue Nguyen.
